{
  "title": "Pesto Saudia Olive Stir-fry",
  "description": "A savory, chewy quick-fix Saudi Arabian dish featuring pepper and olive oil in a pesto sauce made with low FODMAP-friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
  "diet": [
    "sauces-and-pastes",
